Package: wattline-bt
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Keith <keith@kodi.tv>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: bluez-daemon, dbus, kmod-bluetooth
Description: Bluetooth stack dependencies for wattlined (USB BLE dongle). kmod-bluetooth ships btusb.ko for CSR8510-class dongles; note the GL-X3000 kernel lacks the RTL/BCM/MTK btusb sub-drivers, so prefer a generic CSR8510 adapter.
